[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1052","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1052.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1336","title":"3Com HiPerARC 路由器 Telnet 服务 IAC 数据包泛洪拒绝服务漏洞","description":"3Com HiPer Access Router Card (HiperARC) 4.0 至 4.2.29 版本中的 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 Telnet 端口（23/TCP）发送大量 IAC (Interpret As Command) 数据包，导致设备 CPU 过载并触发重启，造成服务不可用。攻击无需认证，仅需网络可达即可实施。该产品已停止维护，无官方补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1336"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-12","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议在边界防火墙上限制对 Telnet 端口（23/TCP）的访问，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接。如业务允许，建议禁用 Telnet 服务并迁移至 SSH 进行远程管理，同时尽快替换为受支持的现代路由设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93458364903256&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93492615408725&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/6057","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1336"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1052.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0321","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0321.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0724","title":"OpenBSD procfs/fdescfs readdir 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 的 procfs 和 fdescfs 文件系统在 readdir() 函数中处理 uio_offset 参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用精心构造的 uio_offset 值触发缓冲区越界写入，导致内核内存损坏，进而实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.5 及更早版本，但 procfs 和 fdescfs 默认未启用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0724"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-12","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 OpenBSD 2.6 或更高版本。对于 OpenBSD 2.5，应用 errata 002 补丁。建议在不必要时禁用 procfs 和 fdescfs 文件系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.openbsd.org/errata25.html","http://www.osvdb.org/6128"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0321.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0875","title":"Microsoft Windows / Solaris ICMP Router Discovery Protocol 默认路由篡改漏洞","description":"ICMP 路由器发现协议（IRDP）存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送伪造的 ICMP 路由器通告报文，修改受影响主机的默认路由表。当运行 Microsoft Windows 98a/98b/98SE 或 Solaris 2.6 的系统启用了 IRDP 时，攻击者无需认证即可将网络流量重定向至恶意主机，进而实施中间人攻击、数据窃听或流量劫持。该漏洞利用门槛低，仅需目标处于同一广播域且 IRDP 处于默认启用状态。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0875"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.373","remediation":"对于 Windows 98 系统，在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\VxD\\DHCP 下将 PerformRouterDiscovery 设为 0 以禁用 IRDP；对于 Solaris 2.6，在 /etc/default/inetinit 中将 IRDP 相关参数禁用或升级至受支持的 Solaris 版本。由于上述系统均已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ216141","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/578","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19451","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0875.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0875.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0875","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0875.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/363.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0875.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5pjr-xvrx-vmj4/GHSA-5pjr-xvrx-vmj4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/icmp-info.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/364.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0667","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0667.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0867","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 HTTP请求畸形标头洪水拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在输入验证不当导致的拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送大量包含畸形 HTTP 请求头的报文，触发 IIS 服务进程崩溃，导致网站无法正常响应合法用户请求。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 及 Microsoft Commercial Internet System 2.0/2.5、Site Server Commerce Edition 3.0 等产品，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，但无法实现代码执行或数据窃取。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0867"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.347","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-029 提供的补丁程序，该补丁修复了 IIS 4.0 对畸形 HTTP 请求头处理不当导致的拒绝服务问题。受影响产品包括 IIS 4.0、Site Server 3.0、Site Server 3.0 Commerce Edition 及 Microsoft Commercial Internet System 2.0/2.5。如无法安装补丁，可在网络边界防火墙或 IIS 中配置限制单个 IP 的并发连接数，并监控异常大量 HTTP 请求以缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238349","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-058.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/579","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-029","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19457","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0867.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0867.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0867","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0867.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0867.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m9hv-pvv3-2735/GHSA-m9hv-pvv3-2735.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0867.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_malformed_request.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0667.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0667.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0667.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0661","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0661.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0861","title":"Microsoft IIS SSL ISAPI 筛选器争用条件信息泄露漏洞","description":"IIS 及其他 Web 服务器中的 SSL ISAPI 筛选器存在竞态条件漏洞。当服务器处理 SSL 加密请求时，由于并发访问控制不当，可能导致某些请求在非安全通道上以明文形式泄露敏感信息。攻击者无需特殊权限，通过向目标服务器发送精心构造的 HTTPS 请求即可利用此漏洞。该漏洞影响运行 IIS 的 Windows NT 4.0 等早期版本系统，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0861"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:12.627","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-053 提供的补丁程序（KB244613），可从 Microsoft Download Center 获取 x86 和 Alpha 版本。对于仍运行 IIS 4.0 的系统，建议升级至 IIS 5.0 或更高版本以彻底消除该争用条件漏洞。如无法升级，可在高流量场景下避免多线程调用 SSL ISAPI 筛选器作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ244613","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-053","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0861.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0861","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0861.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0861.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c76m-g7m9-pfh3/GHSA-c76m-g7m9-pfh3.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0861.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0861.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0661.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0263","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0263.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0694","title":"IBM AIX ptrace 系统调用本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统中的 ptrace 系统调用存在缺陷，本地攻击者可通过向目标系统发起特制的 ptrace 调用来触发该漏洞，导致系统内核崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AIX 多个版本，攻击者需要拥有本地用户权限方可利用，无法远程触发，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0694"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.820","remediation":"安装 IBM AIX APAR IX68314 补丁，或将 AIX 升级至 4.3.3 Maintenance Level 9 及以上版本。如无法立即打补丁，可通过限制非授权用户本地登录、使用 chdev 禁用不必要的调试接口等措施降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-055.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0694.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0694","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0694.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0694.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vg2c-63m3-5wwm/GHSA-vg2c-63m3-5wwm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0694.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84474/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--06fdb7a2-f512-4bc3-ba75-667344476ce2.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0263.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0809","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0809.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0814","title":"Red Hat pump DHCP客户端 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 系统中 pump DHCP 客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 pump 客户端向恶意 DHCP 服务器请求 IP 地址时，攻击者可构造特制的 DHCP 响应数据包触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响配置了 pump DHCP 客户端的 Red Hat Linux 6.x 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过局域网远程触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0814"],"sources":["cve","redhat"],"published":"1999-08-11","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 pump DHCP 客户端至 0.8.12 或更高版本，可运行 rpm -Uvh pump-0.8.12-1.i386.rpm 应用 Red Hat 官方安全公告 RHSA-1999:027 的补丁包。若无法立即升级，建议暂停使用 DHCP 客户端改用静态 IP 配置，或在交换机启用 DHCP 侦听（DHCP Snooping）阻断伪造的 DHCP 响应。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-1999-027.html","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0814"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0809.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0577","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0577.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0813","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9134,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10816}}","description":"Cfingerd 是一款用于替代系统 finger 守护进程的服务程序，当管理员在配置中启用 ALLOW_EXECUTION 选项时，程序会在代表用户执行指定程序前未能正确地降低（drop）自身权限。由于权限处理不当，本地已登录的普通用户可利用该缺陷，通过触发 Cfingerd 以用户身份执行程序的操作，使被执行的程序在仍保留 root 特权的情况下运行，从而提升自身权限至 root，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞仅影响启用了 ALLOW_EXECUTION 功能的 Cfingerd 安装，攻击前提是攻击者已具备目标系统的本地账户访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0813"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.607","remediation":"升级 Cfingerd 至修复该权限提升问题的版本（建议升级到 1.4.3 及以上），或编辑配置文件 cfingerd.conf 将 ALLOW_EXECUTION 选项设为禁用（no）以关闭该功能。若无法立即升级，可暂时移除 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/cfingerd）作为缓解措施，并限制仅可信本地用户访问 finger 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0813","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/442e3d0f3c777e02c70fc200a453fe1f1f8a2431/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0813.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0813","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0813.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/19ba23eb6f8fe22cdd9a46164160f96a7cf3fffd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0813.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hqpc-mh2m-mmv8/GHSA-hqpc-mh2m-mmv8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0813.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88407/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990814.data","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0577.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0233","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0233.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0680","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 存在身份认证绕过漏洞。当客户端在完成身份认证之前建立新连接时，服务器会执行额外的未授权处理操作，远程攻击者无需任何认证即可利用此缺陷向目标系统发送大量连接请求，消耗服务器资源，最终导致终端服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0680"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.027","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-028 提供的补丁，该补丁强制终端服务器在建立连接前完成身份验证，从而阻止未认证的连接请求洪泛攻击。如无法安装补丁，可在防火墙层面过滤 TCP 端口 3389（RDP 默认端口），仅允许可信 IP 地址发起连接。由于 Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238600","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-057.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/571","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-028","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6bde90e50f9c8511feb5459f87a55fa56411bd2c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0680","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0680.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5d448b12fda744aa8491fddc8705260f2b4289f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5bd4fceb27857756215e988f4824b12d3de84ec1/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65vm-7q8v-3p23/GHSA-65vm-7q8v-3p23.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000723.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0233.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0220","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0220.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0676","title":"Sun Solaris 2.6 sdtcm_convert 本地符号链接文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 系统中的 sdtcm_convert 工具在处理临时文件时未进行充分的路径安全检查，存在符号链接（symlink）竞争条件漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建恶意的符号链接，诱使 sdtcm_convert 以特权进程身份覆写任意系统文件，从而导致敏感文件被破坏、权限提升或系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户账户权限，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0676"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.510","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00151 提供的 Solaris 2.6 官方补丁：SPARC 平台安装 105868-xx 系列补丁（最终版 105868-24），x86 平台安装 105869-xx 系列补丁（最终版 105869-21）。由于 Solaris 2.6 已终止技术支持（EOL），强烈建议升级至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11.x 或更高版本以获取持续安全更新。如无法立即打补丁或升级，可临时移除 sdtcm_convert 的 setuid 权限（`chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/sdtcm_convert`）并确保 /tmp 等临时目录设置 sticky bit，限制非授权本地用户的 CDE 工具集访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/575","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=19990809134220.A1191%40hades.chaoz.org","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0676","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0676.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-96rr-v4m6-cxx3/GHSA-96rr-v4m6-cxx3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5088ae3b-1fe3-4296-b335-fed943d90602.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0220.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0218","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0218.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0675","title":"Check Point FireWall-1 3.0/4.0 VPN-1 转发 UDP 数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Check Point FireWall-1 3.0 及 4.0 版本在 VPN-1 模块处理 UDP 数据包时存在缺陷，攻击者可构造并发送特制的 UDP 数据包，经由 VPN-1 隧道转发至目标主机的 0 端口。由于防火墙未能正确校验此类异常数据包，目标主机处理时会发生异常，导致拒绝服务（DoS），使受影响的主机或网络服务中断。该漏洞无需身份认证，远程攻击者只要能够向 VPN 网关发送数据包即可触发，影响运行上述版本并启用 VPN-1 功能的防火墙防护下的主机，可被用于中断正常网络访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0675"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.377","remediation":"建议将 Check Point FireWall-1/VPN-1 升级至 4.0 后续修复版本（如 4.1 及官方 Service Pack）。如暂无法升级，可在防火墙规则中显式丢弃发往内部主机 UDP 端口 0 的报文，并限制仅允许受信任的 VPN 加密隧道流量通过，以阻断经由 VPN-1 转发的恶意 UDP 探测包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1038","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/23615","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/576","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0675.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0675","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0675.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0675.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/525.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-49m4-m2vv-447j/GHSA-49m4-m2vv-447j.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/bad-traffic.rules","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0675.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0218.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0216","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0674","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9190,\"outputTokens\":37,\"totalTokens\":10891}}","description":"BSD 系统的 profil(2) 系统调用存在设计缺陷，本地攻击者可通过结合性能剖析（profiling）机制与 execve 系统调用，修改程序运行时的内部数据空间。由于 profil 在进程调用 execve 后未正确清除或重置剖析缓冲区指针，恶意用户可利用该缺陷向特权程序的内存空间写入任意数据，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.4、OpenBSD 2.5 及 Solaris 7.0 等操作系统，需要攻击者拥有本地登录权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0674"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.237","remediation":"升级到已修复该漏洞的 NetBSD 1.4.1 及以上版本、OpenBSD 2.6 及以上版本以及 Solaris 7 的相应内核补丁（如 Sun 发布的 Solaris 7 安全补丁簇）。如暂无法升级，可通过在 /etc/system 中限制或移除普通用户对 profil(2) 系统调用的访问权限，并收紧本地用户权限、启用内核安全加固（如 OpenBSD 的 securelevel）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-067.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/570","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19447","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0674","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1c705830-ca1e-4514-9f5c-b243a52a463e.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000721.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0409","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0722","title":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器 默认配置远程任意软件包安装漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器默认配置存在安全缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络访问服务器管理接口，利用默认配置中的权限控制缺失，在服务器上安装任意软件包。该漏洞影响 Cobalt RaQ2 系列服务器设备，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需任何认证即可远程执行此操作，可能导致服务器被完全控制或植入恶意软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0722"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.193","remediation":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器已停止维护且不再接收安全更新，建议立即迁移至受支持的服务器平台。如无法迁移，应限制对服务器的网络访问，仅允许受信任 IP 通过防火墙规则访问管理端口（默认 80/443/21/22），并禁用不必要的远程管理功能。同时建议修改默认管理员密码，移除默认共享和匿名访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/558","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0722.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0722","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/6de478c60b9c18d30226296959f4d93e9f74a678/1999/CVE-1999-0722/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd02