es/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0673.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0673","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0673.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0673.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g7pc-52xr-cv98/GHSA-g7pc-52xr-cv98.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0673.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--440ade4d-4913-4536-91e5-248e0757abf6.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0212.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1160","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1160.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1524","title":"Motorola FlowPoint DSL 路由器固件 密码恢复功能暴露导致暴力破解漏洞","description":"FlowPoint DSL 路由器固件 3.0.8 之前版本存在安全设计缺陷，密码恢复功能被错误地暴露在 LAN 或 WAN 网络接口上，而非限制在串行控制台端口。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过网络访问该功能，对 6 位数字恢复密码进行暴力破解，一旦成功即可获得路由器的完全管理权限，进而控制目标设备。该漏洞影响所有运行 3.0.8 之前版本固件的 FlowPoint DSL 路由器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1524"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:37.530","remediation":"将 FlowPoint DSL 路由器的固件升级至 3.0.8 或更高版本以修复密码恢复功能可被远程利用的缺陷。如暂时无法升级，应在边界防火墙或路由器上禁用来自 WAN 侧的远程管理访问，并仅允许通过串口控制台端口使用密码恢复功能，同时对管理登录启用账号锁定与强口令策略以缓解暴力破解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93424680430460&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ce36d0de2f3ddd1d56c222c398df994c8c331b1/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1524.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1524","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1524.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cd1e3d0adf029810963282884bd6480e52b853ac/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1524.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8c75-m5rh-r2vp/GHSA-8c75-m5rh-r2vp.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1524.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87966/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/49a3b38344e5fb98213c282604cbf48964f92580/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--8e32eab3-03e5-4ddc-bd4a-23a5766c069d.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1160.toml"}]